    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Whew, we got threw it somehow..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xb,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...your maneuvers are pretty good. You're very skilled, chum."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x11,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oops, sorry. I should've called you \"miss.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I don't mind. You can call me whatever's easiest for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I'll do that from now on."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Let's go back to the original topic. I still wasn't sure when I first met you, but you fight pretty well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Maybe I should re-evaluate you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, I've also been thinking about how I've started to get used to these things."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Although, a part of me doesn't want to get used to it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I got the impression that I'd never be able to tell if you were awake or asleep, just like Nanaca, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that was supposed to be some kind of compliment...right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "That was my intention. At the very least, you're better suited for this than Nanaca."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "With a little training, you might be able to go out hunting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Hunting... Hmm, I feel like that would be pushing it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "No. Within a tenacious body, lies a healthy mind. I see that you have both."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "A t-tenacious body...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x11,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Setting hunting aside, you should continue to train. It's not like you lose anything from getting stronger..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I-I am still a girl, after all, and I don't know much about being tenacious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I see. If you had the will, I would've been happy to train you, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Umm, well, I'll have to pass..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "(Hmm, there's a slight difference<CR>in our sense of values. I understand<CR>what Juris is saying, but still...)"
        }
    ]
}